  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Sauté onion and garlic in olive oil until translucent.",
    "Add ham and chicken, cooking until browned slightly.",
    "Remove from heat and stir in heavy cream and eggs to create a custard base.",
    "Fold in shredded cheese and roasted vegetables, season with salt and pepper.",
    "Transfer mixture to a baking dish and bake for 30 minutes until bubbly and golden.",
    "Let the casserole rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve hot with a side of sautéed greens or a light salad."
